User should see the item in Cart

elements.name: Register new account with valid data

steps.name: User on the Bukalapak homepage for register
User click "Daftar" for registration
User can input data register for registration at Bukalapak
User click button "Daftar" to create new account
User should see new pop up "Verifikasi Pendaftaran"
User click button "Ya, kirim kode" to get verification code
User should see "Masukkan Kode Rahasia yang diterima via email di:" in pop up
User can input valid verification code
User click button "Verifikasi" to verify and create account
User should see "Akun kamu berhasil dibuat!" in new page
